New Origin version has been opened. As usual, Gatto cannot skip this kind of important moment so he has prepared an event for you. You can collect alphabets while you are playing the game. If you collect each alphabet{C=0xFFFF0000/}'N'{C=0xFF4D0D08/},{C=0xFFFF0000/}'E'{C=0xFF4D0D08/},{C=0xFFFF0000/}'W'{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and bring them to Gatto, he will give you a present.
You can obtain {C=0xFFFF0000/}'O'{C=0xFF4D0D08/},{C=0xFFFF0000/}'N'{C=0xFF4D0D08/}through monster hunting, {C=0xFFFF0000/}'R'{C=0xFF4D0D08/},{C=0xFFFF0000/}'G'{C=0xFF4D0D08/} through kill count box and '{C=0xFFFF0000/}I'{C=0xFF4D0D08/}through production.

