Port of the Winds - Gatto

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The New Origin expansion is now open for business. Gatto has prepared an event for you. Collect one of each of the letters: {C=0xFFFF0000/}'O'{C=0xFF4D0D08/},{C=0xFFFF0000/}'R'{C=0xFF4D0D08/},'{C=0xFFFF0000/}I'{C=0xFF4D0D08/},{C=0xFFFF0000/}'G'{C=0xFF4D0D08/},'{C=0xFFFF0000/}I'{C=0xFF4D0D08/},{C=0xFFFF0000/}'N'{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and trade them for a reward.
{C=0xFFFF0000/}'O'{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and {C=0xFFFF0000/}'N'{C=0xFF4D0D08/} can be obtained by killing monsters, {C=0xFFFF0000/}'R'{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and {C=0xFFFF0000/}'G'{C=0xFF4D0D08/} from Monster Count Chests and '{C=0xFFFF0000/}I'{C=0xFF4D0D08/} can be collected by gathering at the production farm.

