Kazeura Leaf and Dragon footprint

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Gatto

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Gatto says you can trade a Kazeura Leaf and a Dragon footprint for a {C=0xFFFF5917/}NEW ORIGIN Yongha Balloon 1{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. Bring a{C=0xFFFF0000/}Kazeura Leaf and Dragon footprint{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to Gatto to exchange for a balloon.

This is the last step to get a balloon!
Give me your Kazeura Leaf and Dragon Footprint {C=0xFF00863C/}%name%{C=0xFF4D0D08/}
and I will give you a balloon.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Talk to Mohamo in Banshi Gorge

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Banshi Gorge - Jack

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Sneaky Thief Jack has received some information on a valuable treasure Mohamo currently has. The treasure is apparently an ancient relic known as a Jetpack [Omega], it's the key to enter Red Fox Delta. Jack's plan is to steam the treasure while Mohamo is distracted.
Talk to {C=0xFF00863C/}Mohamo{C=0xFF4D0D08/} in {C=0xFF016295/}Banshi Gorge{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and get his full attention so Jack can steal the treasure.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Obtain a Backpack Upgrade Kit from Cetirus in Red Fox Delta


{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Banshi Gorge - Mohamo

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Mohamo has suggested that he is willing to manufacture a Jetpack [Alpha] if I get him a {C=0xFFFF5917/}Backpack Upgrade Kit{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. You can get them from {C=0xFF00863C/}Cetirus{C=0xFF4D0D08/} in {C=0xFF016295/}Red Fox Delta{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. Problem is they're really rare to find! Get one and give it to Mohamo and he will create you a Jetpack [Alpha].

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect a First Aid Acupuncture Set(Bearded Whale Coast)

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Bearded Whale Coast  - Maytry

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect the {C=0xFFFF5917/}First Aid Acupuncture Set{C=0xFF4D0D08/} that Maytry dropped at {C=0xFF016295/}Bearded Whale Coast{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. You might find it by hunting the monsters there? Please try your best to find it.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Deliver 'Wyvern Kyero's Egg' to Amy at Port of the Winds

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Amy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Meet {C=0xFFFF5917/}Amy{C=0xFF4D0D08/} at {C=0xFF016295/}Port of the Winds{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to check on the status of Kyero's Wyvern Egg.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Talk to Great Wizard Edeline

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Edeline

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Find {C=0xFFFF0000/}Edeline{C=0xFF4D0D08/} at {C=0xFF016295/}Port of the Winds{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to check on the status of Kyero's egg.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect the Huge Glass Incubator, Infrared Lamp and Multipurpose electronic device Kit from City Hall Sewer

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Edeline

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
To hatch Kyero's egg, you will need an incubator. The required materials can obtained by killing monsters at {C=0xFF016295/}City Hall Sewer{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. Obtain 1 Huge Glass Incubator, 5 {C=0xFFFF0000/}Infrared Lamps{C=0xFF4D0D08/} and 2  {C=0xFFFF0000/}Multipurpose electronic device Kits{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. You must wear the {C=0xFFFF0000/}Emergency Gas Mask{C=0xFF4D0D08/} given to you by {C=0xFF00863C/}Edeline{C=0xFF4D0D08/}.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Talk to Pet Merchant Amy at Port of the Winds

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Amy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The incubator to hatch the Wyvern egg is ready. However, there is not much time left before the Wyvern hatches, so you better ask {C=0xFF00863C/}Amy{C=0xFF4D0D08/} which food is best to feed Wyvern when it does.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Talk to Great Wizard Edeline

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of the Winds - Edeline

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Now you have received the food for your Wyvern, find Great Wizard {C=0xFF00863C/}Edeline{C=0xFF4D0D08/} at {C=0xFF016295/}Port of the Winds{C=0xFF4D0D08/} to check on the Wyvern's egg hatching.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Talk to Archpriest Ganu of Kazeura at Jigsaw Pincers Coast

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Jigsaw Pincers Coast - Ganu

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
We have lost contact with {C=0xFF00863C/}Archpriest Ganu of Kazeura{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. He was last known to be somewhere around {C=0xFF016295/}Jigsaw Pincers Coast{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. Try and find him.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Obtain 10 Crabby Sticks in Jigsaw Pincers Coast

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Jigsaw Pincers Coast - Ganu

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The only way to save the Dragon Tribe's Old Man from starving is by finding 10 {C=0xFFFF5917/}Crabby Sticks{C=0xFF4D0D08/} from Crabbies in {C=0xFF016295/}Jigsaw Pincers Coast{C=0xFF4D0D08/}. Hurry up

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
